ZORRO (1957) 6-9 

6. Zorro Saves a Friend  11/14/1957
When Captain Monastario arrests the fugitive Torres&#039; wife and daughter, hoping to catch Zorro trying to rescue them, he instead catches Don Diego&#039;s chief vacquero Benito, who is in love with the daughter Elena.
  Stars: Guy Williams (Don Diego de la Vega / El Zorro), Gene Sheldon (Bernardo) ,George J. Lewis (Don Alejandro de la Vega), Henry Calvin (Sgt. Garcia), Don Diamond (Cpl. Reyes) 
  Guest star: Britt Lomond (Captain Monastario), Romney Brent (Padre Felipe), Eugenia Paul (Senorita Elena Torres), Than Wyenn (Licenciado Pina) , Madeleine Holmes (Dona Luisa Torres), Pat Hogan (Benito)

7. Monastario Sets a Trap   11/21/1957 
Learning that a group of disgruntled landowners plan to seize the cuartel and free the political prisoners, Captain Monastario sets a trap to capture them, including Zorro&#039;s father Don Alejandro.
  Guest star: Britt Lomond (Captain Monastario), Than Wyenn (Licenciado Pina), Eugenia Paul (Senorita Elena Torres) , Madeleine Holmes (Dona Luisa Torres)

8. Zorro&#039;s Ride into Terror  11/28/1957 
After Zorro hides his wounded father in the secret cave, as Don Diego he must divert Captain Monastario and his soldiers who are searching for the old man.
  Guest star: Britt Lomond (Captain Monastario), Jan Arvan (Don Ignacio Torres)

9. A Fair Trial   12/5/1957 
With his father Don Alejandro now charged with treason along with Don Torres, Zorro must see that the judge sent by the governor arrives to assure a fair trial.
  Guest star: Britt Lomond (Captain Monastario), Jan Arvan (Don Ignacio Torres), Than Wyenn (Licenciado Pina) , Sebastian Cabot (Judge Vasca), William Schallert (Innkeeper)
